content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11ยง 23.3 - Accident and health insurance agents for property/casualty companies

State Regulations

Applicants for licensees to act as agents with respect to accident and health insurance on behalf of property/casualty insurance companies shall be required to take the accident and health examination under Part 22 of this Title. Notes
